      "id": "130641",
      "key": "SFPSCA-3308",
      "summary": "Setting GitLab projects criticality",
      "description": "h1. Overview\n\nRIC DevOps team asked for defining criticality of our Client360 GitLab projects. They had described the entire topic in [https://richemont-cds.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/GTCDS/pages/113884769/GitLab+-+Governance#Project-Criticality|https://richemont-cds.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/GTCDS/pages/113884769/GitLab+-+Governance#Project-Criticality|smart-link]. I’ve attached an email with their request too.\n\nI’ve discussed the criticality with Bogdan and Quentin and as a result, our main Salesforce-Master repository is given medium criticality. Even if the repository is down, we still have a break-the-glass solution - [link|https://richemont.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RCRM/pages/463966721/Reclaim+legacy+release+management+access+GitLab+pipelines+service+outage] - that enables running production deploys.\n\nh1. Action\n\nAs an GitLab group owner, go to [https://gitlab.richemont.com/groups/scm_project/ric/client360/-/security/compliance_dashboard/projects|https://gitlab.richemont.com/groups/scm_project/ric/client360/-/security/compliance_dashboard/projects] and set the following project criticality:\n\nh2. Criticality:Medium\n\nGiven to: Salesforce-Master & Tools.\n\nSalesforce-Master is the only project we use for deployment to Salesforce orgs (Qual, Val, Prod).\n\nTools includes several non-critical automations, yet they enable some features or facilitate daily operations.\n\nh2. Criticality:Low\n\nAssigned to all other projects. They are forks of Salesforce-master.\n\nh2. Criticality:NotSpecified\n\nAssigned to 2 new projects that don’t have a precise objective yet.\n\nh1. Sonarqube rollout\n\nProject criticality defines the timeline for rolling out SonarQube, offered by the same team who requested defining project criticality. More info in [https://richemont-cds.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/GTCDS/pages/113997621/QnT+-+Roadmap+KPIs#CODE-QUALITY|https://richemont-cds.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/GTCDS/pages/113997621/QnT+-+Roadmap+KPIs#CODE-QUALITY|smart-link].",
